Â  <h3>Set seeds</h3>
Â  <pre>
Â  SEEDS="258f523c96efde50d5fe0a9faeea8a3e83be22ca@seed.circulus-1.empower.aviaone.com:20272,<br>d6a7cd9fa2bafc0087cb606de1d6d71216695c25@51.159.161.174:26656,<br>babc3f3f7804933265ec9c40ad94f4da8e9e0017@testnet-seed.rhinostake.com:17456"
